1
TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Nghin cu v pht trin ng dng trn nn tng Floodlight Controller ca
chun m Open Flow
Tc gi lun vn: Phm Hong Hng Kha: 2012B
Ngi hng dn: PGS.TS. Ng Hng Sn
NI DUNG TM TT
1. L do chn ti
V xu hng v kh nng pht trin ln ca kin trc SDN, ti quyt nh chn
ti Nghin cu v pht trin ng dng trn nn tng Floodlight Controller ca
chun m Open Flow lm ti cho lun vn thc s ca mnh.
2. Mc ch, i tng, phm vi nghin cu.
Mc ch chnh ca ti khi la chn ti lun vn gm:
- Nm bt c kin trc SDN v cc thnh phn trong kin trc ny. Sau qu
trnh tm hiu ban u ti la chn Floodlight Controller v OpenFlow lm hai
cng ngh nn tng cho qu trnh nghin cu tip theo ca mnh.
- Xy dng h thng m phng v pht trin mt ng dng c th phc v
nghin cu.
- Tm hiu cc hng ng dng cng ngh kin trc SDN vo thc t, pht
trin cc ng dng s dng cng ngh kin trc ny.
3. Ni dung chnh lun vn
Ni dung lun vn bao gm 04 chng:
Chng 1: Hin trng h thng mng v xu hng cng ngh (a ra
nhng khuyt im cn tn ti ca cc h thng mng ph bin hin nay ch ra l
do cn phi c mt kin trc mng mi v gii thiu tng quan v kin trc SDN. Sau
ti s trnh by c th v nhng vn cn tn ti vi bi ton thit lp, thay i
policy based routing t ng theo thi gian trong h thng mng ph bin hin nay v
nh hng gii php cho bi ton ny).
Chng 2: La chn cng ngh (Trnh by v qu trnh la chn cng ngh
gii quyt bi ton vi gii php la chn trong Chng 1).
2
Chng 3: Qu trnh thc hin (Trnh by c th qu trnh thc hin m
phng cng nh pht trin ng dng mi).
Chng 4: nh gi hiu qu (So snh hiu qu gia kin trc SDN s dng
ng dng pht trin v kin trc mng truyn thng trong vic gii quyt bi ton
thit lp, thay i Policy Base Routing t ng theo thi gian trn cc thit b trong h
thng).
4. Phng php nghin cu
Trong qu trnh thc hin lun vn ti s dng hai phng php nghin cu gm:
- Nghin cu l thuyt (Nghin cu cc ti liu, cng ngh lin quan; Tng
hp, la chn cng ngh).
- M phng thc nghim (Phn tch a ra phng n m phng thc nghim;
Xy dng h thng gi lp v phn mm ng dng; nh gi kt qu t c).
5. Kt lun
Kt qu t c
- Nm bt c kin thc v SDN v mt s phng php m phng nghin
cu v SDN.
- Thit lp c mt m hnh gi lp, tuy cn n gin nhng cng c th minh
ha cho tim nng s dng ca SDN.
- Pht trin thm c thnh phn chc nng thit lp, thay i policy based
routing t ng theo thi gian cho mt phn mm m ngun m.
- So snh, nh gi hiu qu vic thit lp, thay i policy based routing t
ng theo thi gian gia h thng mng s dng kin trc SDN v h thng mng
thng dng hin nay.
Nhc im cn tn ti
- Sn phm ng dng pht trin cn n gin, v vn cn tn ti mt s li
nh cha hon thin.
- Cha th nghim c sn phm (ng dng thit lp, thay i policy based
routing t ng theo thi gian) trn mt h thng mng thc t.
3
- Cha nh lng ha c phn nh gi hiu qu ca h thng mng s dng
kin trc SDN trong vic gii quyt bi ton thit lp, thay i policy based routing t
ng theo thi gian.
Phm vi ng dng
V SDN l cng ngh mi, hin ti phn ln h thng thit b mng vn cha h
tr SDN nn phm vi ng dng trong thc t ca lun vn l cha ln. Hin ti, lun
vn ca ti c th ng dng trong vic nghin cu v cng ngh kin trc SDN trong
thi gian tip theo, ngoi ra ng dng m ngun m ti ang xy dng hon ton c
th tip tc pht trin hon thin hn.
nh hng nghin cu pht trin
Phm vi ng dng trong thc t ca lun vn cha ln nhng n cho thy tim
nng rt ln ca kin trc SDN trong vn qun l h thng mng ni chung v iu
khin lung d liu ni ring. ti ca ti c th tip tc pht trin theo hng
nghin cu m rng v iu khin lung d liu theo lu lng thc t h thng.
